          <p class="text-gray-600 text-center mb-6">Step-by-step instructions for all PropertyCRM features</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <li>• Getting started guide</li>
            <li>• Property management basics</li>
            <li>• Lead tracking workflows</li>
            <li>• Team collaboration features</li>
            <li>• Reporting and analytics</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="bg-green-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 text-center">API Reference</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-center mb-6">Complete technical documentation for developers</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <li>• REST API endpoints</li>
            <li>• Authentication methods</li>
            <li>• Data models & schemas</li>
            <li>• Webhook integrations</li>
            <li>• Code examples & SDKs</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="bg-purple-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
